		<author>
			<name>Mark Corti</name>
			<email>web@maidstonecanoeclub.net</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Unbelievably, the last week of the summer holidays is just around the corner. &amp;nbsp;Cue tears from children and teachers alike, and possibly tears of happiness from parents! &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Luckily, we've got just the things to finish the summer break off in style: a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar/eventdetail/41120/26|29|30|31|32|39|43/beginner-course-session-1-4&quot;&gt;1-day beginner's kayaking course&lt;/a&gt;! &amp;nbsp;Spend the last Friday of summer on the water and make it one to remember. &amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar/eventdetail/41120/26|29|30|31|32|39|43/beginner-course-session-1-4&quot;&gt;Spaces still available - Friday August 25th&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
