	<entry>
		<title>Apocalypse When?</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1358-apocalypse-when"/>
		<published>2023-08-13T11:27:43+01:00</published>
		<updated>2023-08-13T11:27:43+01:00</updated>
		<id>https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1358-apocalypse-when</id>
		<author>
			<name>Mark Corti</name>
			<email>web@maidstonecanoeclub.net</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Tuesday is - of course - the anniversary of the release of Apocalypse Now, and we will - of course - be &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar/eventdetail/41084/26|29|30|31|32|39|43/pool-session&quot;&gt;commemorating this at the pool session&lt;/a&gt;, possibly with a rousing chorus of Ride of the Valkyries. &amp;nbsp;Although we can't promise the smell of napalm in the morning, we can promise the scent of chlorine in our wam, clean pool! &amp;nbsp;It's also &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/lemon-meringue-pie-day/&quot;&gt;National Lemon Meringue Pie&lt;/a&gt; day.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Tuesday is - of course - the anniversary of the release of Apocalypse Now, and we will - of course - be &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar/eventdetail/41084/26|29|30|31|32|39|43/pool-session&quot;&gt;commemorating this at the pool session&lt;/a&gt;, possibly with a rousing chorus of Ride of the Valkyries. &amp;nbsp;Although we can't promise the smell of napalm in the morning, we can promise the scent of chlorine in our wam, clean pool! &amp;nbsp;It's also &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/lemon-meringue-pie-day/&quot;&gt;National Lemon Meringue Pie&lt;/a&gt; day.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
