	</entry>
	<entry>
		<title>FSRT / Paddlesport Safety &amp; Rescue Course</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1357-fsrt-paddlesport-safety-rescue-course"/>
		<published>2023-08-12T11:41:48+01:00</published>
		<updated>2023-08-12T11:41:48+01:00</updated>
		<id>https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1357-fsrt-paddlesport-safety-rescue-course</id>
		<author>
			<name>Mark Corti</name>
			<email>web@maidstonecanoeclub.net</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;2023's only (probably!) Safety &amp;amp; Rescue course starts on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/eventdetail/41107/-/paddlesport-safety-rescue-course-psrc-was-fsrt&quot;&gt;Wednesday 23rd August at 6pm&lt;/a&gt;. &amp;nbsp;This course is a huge amount of fun, at least if you do it in the summer! &amp;nbsp;It's also the most useful training you'll do, giving you skills and confidence to keep yourself and your paddle buddies out of trouble on the water, and to perform effective rescues with minimal physical effort. &amp;nbsp;(This course is also a pre-requisite for any Instructor, Coaching and many Leadership awards).&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;2023's only (probably!) Safety &amp;amp; Rescue course starts on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/eventdetail/41107/-/paddlesport-safety-rescue-course-psrc-was-fsrt&quot;&gt;Wednesday 23rd August at 6pm&lt;/a&gt;. &amp;nbsp;This course is a huge amount of fun, at least if you do it in the summer! &amp;nbsp;It's also the most useful training you'll do, giving you skills and confidence to keep yourself and your paddle buddies out of trouble on the water, and to perform effective rescues with minimal physical effort. &amp;nbsp;(This course is also a pre-requisite for any Instructor, Coaching and many Leadership awards).&lt;/p&gt;</content>
		<category term="News" />
	</entry>
