	<entry>
		<title>Frontier Sapiens - Outdoor Cinema Adventure Films</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1353-frontier-sapiens-outdoor-cinema-adventure-films"/>
		<published>2023-07-06T18:32:14+01:00</published>
		<updated>2023-07-06T18:32:14+01:00</updated>
		<id>https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1353-frontier-sapiens-outdoor-cinema-adventure-films</id>
		<author>
			<name>Mark Corti</name>
			<email>web@maidstonecanoeclub.net</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Outdoor movies at an outdoor cinema? &amp;nbsp;Yes please! &amp;nbsp;New fi;m bestival Frontier Sapiens is in Canterbury this August 24th. &amp;nbsp;Featureing 100ft waterfall drops, a world-first expedition in the Karakoram mountains, and a 250km journey in traditional Mokoro canoes through hippo-infested waters, it promises to be a fantastic evening out. &amp;nbsp;Catch the&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HipvZZh898U&quot;&gt; trailer here&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/outdoor-cinema-frontier-sapiens-film-festival-canterbury-tickets-564598548457&quot;&gt;book online here&lt;/a&gt;. &amp;nbsp; See you there! &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Outdoor movies at an outdoor cinema? &amp;nbsp;Yes please! &amp;nbsp;New fi;m bestival Frontier Sapiens is in Canterbury this August 24th. &amp;nbsp;Featureing 100ft waterfall drops, a world-first expedition in the Karakoram mountains, and a 250km journey in traditional Mokoro canoes through hippo-infested waters, it promises to be a fantastic evening out. &amp;nbsp;Catch the&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HipvZZh898U&quot;&gt; trailer here&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/outdoor-cinema-frontier-sapiens-film-festival-canterbury-tickets-564598548457&quot;&gt;book online here&lt;/a&gt;. &amp;nbsp; See you there! &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
		<category term="News" />
	</entry>
	<entry>
		<title>Forward Paddling for the rest of us!</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1349-forward-paddling-for-the-rest-of-us"/>
		<published>2023-06-17T10:48:32+01:00</published>
		<updated>2023-06-17T10:48:32+01:00</updated>
		<id>https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1349-forward-paddling-for-the-rest-of-us</id>
		<author>
			<name>Mark Corti</name>
			<email>web@maidstonecanoeclub.net</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Most of us go forward most of the time! &amp;nbsp;By making a couple of simple changes to the way you paddle, you can do it with less effort - maybe even go faster or further, if you want to! &amp;nbsp;Joel Cameron is running a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/eventdetail/40314/-/forward-paddling-for-touring-bimbling&quot;&gt;fun session to help with this on July 12th&lt;/a&gt; - please sign up in advance so he knows how many to expect.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Most of us go forward most of the time! &amp;nbsp;By making a couple of simple changes to the way you paddle, you can do it with less effort - maybe even go faster or further, if you want to! &amp;nbsp;Joel Cameron is running a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/eventdetail/40314/-/forward-paddling-for-touring-bimbling&quot;&gt;fun session to help with this on July 12th&lt;/a&gt; - please sign up in advance so he knows how many to expect.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
		<category term="News" />
	</entry>
	<entry>
		<title>Intro to Whitewater</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1350-intro-to-whitewater"/>
		<published>2023-06-17T10:53:01+01:00</published>
		<updated>2023-06-17T10:53:01+01:00</updated>
		<id>https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1350-intro-to-whitewater</id>
		<author>
			<name>Mark Corti</name>
			<email>web@maidstonecanoeclub.net</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;If you fancy moving on to moving water (see what I did there?), then our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/eventdetail/40278/-/introduction-to-whitewater-weekend&quot;&gt;amazing Intro to Whitewater weekend&lt;/a&gt; on the lovely River Dee in North Wales is for you! &amp;nbsp;We'll spend the weekend working on techniques to have fun on the rapids while staying in control. &amp;nbsp;You should ideally have done the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/eventdetail/40291/-/flatwater-skills-for-dynamic-water-progression&quot;&gt;Flatwater Skills for Dynamic Water Progression course&lt;/a&gt; beforehand (or have the skills covered), but drop me a line if you haven't and we can have a chat.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;If you fancy moving on to moving water (see what I did there?), then our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/eventdetail/40278/-/introduction-to-whitewater-weekend&quot;&gt;amazing Intro to Whitewater weekend&lt;/a&gt; on the lovely River Dee in North Wales is for you! &amp;nbsp;We'll spend the weekend working on techniques to have fun on the rapids while staying in control. &amp;nbsp;You should ideally have done the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/eventdetail/40291/-/flatwater-skills-for-dynamic-water-progression&quot;&gt;Flatwater Skills for Dynamic Water Progression course&lt;/a&gt; beforehand (or have the skills covered), but drop me a line if you haven't and we can have a chat.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
		<category term="News" />
	</entry>
	<entry>
		<title>Kent and beyond</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1352-kent-and-beyond"/>
		<published>2023-06-19T06:31:41+01:00</published>
		<updated>2023-06-19T06:31:41+01:00</updated>
		<id>https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1352-kent-and-beyond</id>
		<author>
			<name>Mark Corti</name>
			<email>web@maidstonecanoeclub.net</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Beult. The Swale. Stour. Hammer Stream. Rother. And there are dozens more besides just in Kent!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;if you'd like to stretch your paddling legs but aren't sure where to start, then sign up for the Explore or Touring Awards running in the next few weeks. They'll give you the knowledge and confidence you need to paddle further afield - and teach you some skills to boot! &amp;nbsp;See the calendar for dates and to book.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Beult. The Swale. Stour. Hammer Stream. Rother. And there are dozens more besides just in Kent!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;if you'd like to stretch your paddling legs but aren't sure where to start, then sign up for the Explore or Touring Awards running in the next few weeks. They'll give you the knowledge and confidence you need to paddle further afield - and teach you some skills to boot! &amp;nbsp;See the calendar for dates and to book.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
		<category term="News" />
	</entry>
	<entry>
		<title>New course dates released</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1351-new-course-dates-released"/>
		<published>2023-06-18T08:45:57+01:00</published>
		<updated>2023-06-18T08:45:57+01:00</updated>
		<id>https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/1351-new-course-dates-released</id>
		<author>
			<name>Mark Corti</name>
			<email>web@maidstonecanoeclub.net</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;As Ratty famously said in &lt;em&gt;The Wind in the Willows&lt;/em&gt;, there is nothing - absolutely nothing - half so much worth doing as simply messing about in boats! &amp;nbsp;That goes double when the weather is as gorgeous as it has been for the last few weeks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We've just added &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/0/0/43&quot;&gt;more beginner course dates&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/2023/7/43&quot;&gt;July&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/2023/8/43&quot;&gt;August&lt;/a&gt; - check the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/0/0/43&quot;&gt;website for details and to book online&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our legendary Junior Paddle Club is also going from strength to strength, with new-paddler inductions every Tuesday evening - again, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/0/0/43&quot;&gt;booking is open online&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We look forward to seeing you on the river!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/media/com_acymailing/images/statpicture.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;1&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;As Ratty famously said in &lt;em&gt;The Wind in the Willows&lt;/em&gt;, there is nothing - absolutely nothing - half so much worth doing as simply messing about in boats! &amp;nbsp;That goes double when the weather is as gorgeous as it has been for the last few weeks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We've just added &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/0/0/43&quot;&gt;more beginner course dates&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/2023/7/43&quot;&gt;July&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/2023/8/43&quot;&gt;August&lt;/a&gt; - check the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/0/0/43&quot;&gt;website for details and to book online&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our legendary Junior Paddle Club is also going from strength to strength, with new-paddler inductions every Tuesday evening - again, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/index.php/calendar-side/monthcalendar/0/0/43&quot;&gt;booking is open online&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We look forward to seeing you on the river!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.maidstonecanoeclub.net/joomla/media/com_acymailing/images/statpicture.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;1&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
		<category term="News" />
	</entry>
